  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">KBB CES Program - Education</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Development Objective
To promote education for learners with visual impairment in mainstream schools in Kenya

Specific Objectives:
1. To increase access to education for VIC in mainstream schools in each of the 3 counties by 30% by 2015
2. To enhance the quality of education for VIC in mainstream schools in each of the 19 KIEP Counties by 2015
3. To develop &amp; integrate a reliable data-base on Children With Disabilities (CWD) within the National Education MIS by 2015
4. To advocate for the development and/or implementation of policies and practices that promote the rights of CWD to quality education by 2015</narrative>
  </description>
